<plot>Rachel Miller (Jane Eden), a successful children's illustrator, moves to rural Italy immediately after the sudden death of her husband. She knows little of the language and less of the culture. We observe Rachel as she begins her reluctant recovery, unaided by her self imposed isolation.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?253013</url></doc>
